79
00:06:18,104 --> 00:06:22,315
I mean, she raises the kids,
she decorates, she...

80
00:06:22,441 --> 00:06:27,020
Well, I don't know what the hell she does,
but she takes care of things.

81
00:06:28,530 --> 00:06:30,570
I guess...

82
00:06:30,699 --> 00:06:33,818
