198
00:14:54,127 --> 00:14:58,374
Look, miss. Miss! I'm in the middle of
a major meeting. Keep her quiet, OK?

199
00:14:58,506 --> 00:15:01,840
- Look, if it's so easy, you try it!
- I don't know how to...

200
00:15:01,968 --> 00:15:04,210
