00:16:52,863 --> 00:16:56,481
22... Oh, 22 pounds. OK.

229
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:07,039
Oh, my God.

230
00:17:08,836 --> 00:17:10,995
There.

231
00:17:11,547 --> 00:17:13,172
Hi.

232
00:17:14,049 --> 00:17:15,841
Hi.

